Environment:
============
pyenv install 3.6.8

Run code:
=========
git clone https://github.com/aimin-tang/2020_python.git ./examine
cd examine/minion_game
pipenv install
pipenv shell
python minion_game.py

Run tests (after you run code):
===============================
cd examine/minion_game
export PYTHONPATH=.
pytest -v tests/unittest

Cleanup:
========
pipenv --rm
exit
cd examine/..
rm -rf examine